code:
graph TD
    subgraph "Tree Detection"
        PLR[HealthTech_EMR_Sync] --> SCAN[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
        SCAN --> LOGS[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
        LOGS --> CLUSTER[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
        CLUSTER --> BASE[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
        BASE --> CHECK{HealthTech_EMR_Sync}
        CHECK -->|No| ADD[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
        CHECK -->|Yes| SKIP[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
        ADD --> TREES[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    end
    
    subgraph "Tree Cutting Process"
        REQ[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine] --> LLM[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
        LLM --> COORD[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
        COORD --> MOVE[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
        MOVE --> START[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
        
        START --> HEIGHT[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
        HEIGHT --> FINDLOGS[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
        FINDLOGS --> HASLOG{HealthTech_LabAnalyzer}
        
        HASLOG -->|Yes| CUT[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
        HASLOG -->|No| NEXTH[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
        
        CUT --> EFFECTS[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
        EFFECTS --> WOOD[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
        WOOD --> MORE{HealthTech_LabAnalyzer}
        
        MORE -->|Yes| HEIGHT
        MORE -->|No| NEXTH
        
        NEXTH --> MAXH{HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine}
        MAXH -->|No| HEIGHT
        MAXH -->|Yes| DONE[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
        
        DONE --> MARK[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
        MARK --> COMPLETE[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    end
    
    subgraph "Cut Tree Registry"
        MARK --> REGISTRY[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
        REGISTRY --> KEY[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
        KEY --> PERSIST[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
        PERSIST --> PREVENT[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    end
    
    style SCAN fill:#e8f5e8
    style CUT fill:#ffebee
    style EFFECTS fill:#fff3e0
    style REGISTRY fill:#f3e5f5
repo_description: Intelligent Agentic NPCs for Minecraft with LLM Integration
